The 2012 Summer Olympics closing ceremony is held, featuring a celebration of British pop music and the handover of the Olympic Flag to the Mayor of Rio de Janeiro in preparation for the 2016 Games. (BBC)Bradley Wiggins and Dave Brailsford are awarded knighthoods in the 2013 New Year Honours list, while Sarah Storey becomes a Dame, the female equivalent of a knight. (The Guardian) (The Daily Telegraph) (Road.cc)